    <title>Drupal 8 for Non-Developers</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/drupal-8-non-developers</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Drupal 8 is right around the corner and unless you have either been involved in Code Sprints or even know what a Code Sprint is then this session is for you. &amp;nbsp;I will take us on a journey of all the scary things that Non-Developers fear&amp;nbsp;and bring us out into the world of Developers lingo, thinking and strategies. &amp;nbsp;After this session you will be able to overcome your&amp;nbsp;Octophobia and walk and talk Drupal 8 with the best of them.&lt;/p&gt;

