  <item>
    <title>Portaging Around the Waterfall: Building an API with Scrum</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/portaging-around-waterfall-building-api-scrum</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Not all projects in the public sector have to follow the traditional waterfall lifecycle.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;When NIAID asked Squishymedia to help&amp;nbsp;add an API to the &lt;a href=&quot;http://3dprint.nih.gov/&quot;&gt;3DPrint.nih.gov&lt;/a&gt; site it seemed like an ideal project for an agile scrum methodology, so we dove right in and tried it. &amp;nbsp;Did the scrum team successfully portage the project canoe&amp;nbsp;around the waterfall?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this session we&#039;ll discuss:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A brief description of scrum and&amp;nbsp;the project.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Why we thought scrum was the right tool for this project.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;How we adapted scrum to fit the project.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Scrum, estimating, and budgeting.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;What worked, and what didn&#039;t.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;What agencies and contractors can do to facilitate a successful agile project.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;What we thought would happen ... and what really happened.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;gchaix&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item odd&quot;&gt;meghan.coakley@nih.gov&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-og-vocabulary field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Track:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Session Tracks (Drupal GovCon 2015)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/session-tracks-drupal-govcon-2015/business-and-strategy&quot;&gt;Business and Strategy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
