    <title>Hosting Options and Performance Improvements</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/hosting-options-and-performance-improvements</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to choose from the variety of hosting levels and provider offerings. There are a myriad of options from shared hosting, VPS, managed instances, dedicated servers, and Drupal-specific providers.&lt;/p&gt;

