  <item>
    <title>Website Redesign in Drupal: are you planning to succeed or succeeding to fail. It all starts with your RFP</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/website-redesign-drupal-are-you-planning-succeed-or-succeeding-fail-it</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Are you currently using, or considering Drupal? Whether you are looking to develop an organization&#039;s initial website or upgrade an existing one, managing a website development project can be a daunting task, especially if your organization lacks internal website design and development expertise. Drupal provides an extremely flexible platform, but determining an appropriate approach to best fit your organization&#039;s needs and budget often involves navigating the benefits and costs of different providers, approaches, and technologies.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Join us for a fresh look at the planning, RFP writing, and hiring process specifically tailored for Drupal websites. We&#039;ll provide a &quot;from the trenches&quot; look at common points of failure and provide tactics for avoiding them through guidelines, tips, case studies, and role-play.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Takeaways:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Learn how to plan a successful Drupal website project&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Learn how to prepare an appropriate RFP and address Drupal specific questions&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Learn how to select appropriate internal resources and/or external vendors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-slides field--type-file field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Slides:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;file-icon&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;application/pdf&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/sites/2015.drupalgovcon.org/files/slides/Website%20Redesign%20in%20Drupal_%20are%20you%20planning%20to%20succeed%20or%20succeeding%20to%20fail.%20It%20all%20starts%20with%20your%20RFP-DesignHammer.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=7724892&quot;&gt;Website Redesign in Drupal_ are you planning to succeed or succeeding to fail. It all starts with your RFP-DesignHammer.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;stephen@designhammer.com&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item odd&quot;&gt;david@designhammer.com&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-session-timeslot field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Time Slot(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div 