    <title>Hello Gulp - Have You Met Drupal?</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/hello-gulp-have-you-met-drupal</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preprocess. Lint. Minify.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Many repetitive tasks go into building quality sites - tasks that take time and consideration. Task that can be automated.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you are tired of running through a plethora of steps to ready code for deployment, task runners are for you.&lt;/p&gt;

