    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn the basics of using Drupal Features (Drupal 7) for configuration management, version control, and collaborative development.&lt;/p&gt;

