    <title>Surviving Life as a Remote Web Worker</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/surviving-life-remote-web-worker</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;No one wants to admit it, but working remote is hard. You have to collaborate with people you might never meet over a spotty&amp;nbsp;VPN connection with the added (often self-imposed)&amp;nbsp;pressure of having non-stop productive days. ALL this&amp;nbsp;while chasing the work-life balance unicorn. It&#039;s not easy, but it is doable. In this session, you&#039;ll learn how to play up your personal strengths to go the distance in a non-traditional work setup. We&#039;ll also cover tips and techniques to get the most out of working remote and how to avoid common pitfalls like the &quot;freshman 40&quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Sara.cope@va.gov&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-og-vocabulary field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Track:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Session Tracks (Drupal GovCon 2015)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/session-tracks-drupal-govcon-2015/business-and-strategy&quot;&gt;Business and Strategy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
