  <item>
    <title>Section 508 and Usability</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/section-508-and-usability</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;This session will be an overview of Section 508 of the Rehabilitation Act and Usability. &amp;nbsp;How does Section 508 affect your environment?&amp;nbsp; How does Usability fit into the Section 508 environment? What do I need to know to help with implementing both of these? &amp;nbsp;How do I get the tools and resources I need to do this? &amp;nbsp;How do I find out the POCs that can help me? &amp;nbsp;And much, much more.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So don&#039;t miss this&amp;nbsp;opportunity to come and learn more about Section 508 and usability and ask questions!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-slides field--type-file field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Slides:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;file-icon&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;application/pdf&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/sites/2015.drupalgovcon.org/files/slides/Section508-and-Usability-ChamberlainHelen-DrupalGovCon%202015.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=3118478&quot;&gt;Section508-and-Usability-ChamberlainHelen-DrupalGovCon 2015.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;helen.chamberlain@gsa.gov&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-session-timeslot field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Time Slot(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots clearfix&quot; class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-timeslot-time field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Time:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;07/23/2015 - 14:00-07/23/2015 - 14:45&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-timeslot-room field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Room:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Auditorium&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-og-vocabulary field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Track:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Session Tracks (Drupal GovCon 2015)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/session-tracks-drupal-govcon-2015/front-end-user-experience-and-design&quot;&gt;Front-end, User Experience and Design&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
     <pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2015 21:59:29 +0000</pubDate>
