    <title>Exporting Your Data Outside Drupal</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/exporting-your-data-outside-drupal</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;A demonstration of using the Views Data Export module in conjunction with the Views module; to pull out data from a site and export it in different formats (CSV, XLS, DOC, TXT, XML, etc.) for use outside of Drupal. 

