  <item>
    <title>Painting a Perfect Picture with Gesso</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/painting-perfect-picture-gesso</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Learn how to design and theme Drupal sites using &lt;a href=&quot;http://patternlab.io/about.html&quot;&gt;Atomic Design&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.drupal.org/node/1887918&quot;&gt;Drupal 8 CSS architecture guidelines&lt;/a&gt;. At Forum One, we created the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.drupal.org/project/gesso&quot;&gt;Gesso&lt;/a&gt; theme to vastly improve Drupal’s default markup and styles, giving us a nice clean canvas to start each Drupal project with. We also created a version of &lt;a href=&quot;http://patternlab.io/&quot;&gt;Pattern Lab&lt;/a&gt; that outputs the same markup and styles as the Gesso theme, allowing us to quickly design and prototype reusable design components, layouts, and pages.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;Topics Covered&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Design for Drupal with &lt;a href=&quot;http://patternlab.io/&quot;&gt;Pattern Lab&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Organize your &lt;a href=&quot;http://sass-lang.com/&quot;&gt;Sass&lt;/a&gt; and design components&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Leverage &lt;a href=&quot;https://smacss.com/&quot;&gt;SMACSS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://bem.info/method/&quot;&gt;BEM&lt;/a&gt; to write maintainable CSS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Slides:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://dcmouyard.github.io/painting-with-gesso/&quot;&gt;dcmouyard.github.io/painting-with-gesso&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Advanced&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;dcmouyard&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-session-timeslot field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Time Slot(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots clearfix&quot; class=&quot;entity entity-field-collection-item field-collection-item-field-event-timeslots&quot;&gt;
