  <item>
    <title>Case Study: Our Requirements Gathering Toolkit - Surveys; Polls &amp; Visualizing Responses !</title>
    <link>http://2015.drupalgovcon.org/drupal-govcon-2015/sessions/case-study-our-requirements-gathering-toolkit-surveys-polls-visualizing</link>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;We will talk about how we succesfully built a social intranet without actually documenting the requirements (not really!). Our team created a series of custom surveys based on workshops with 8&amp;nbsp;different deparments, and have these varied team&amp;nbsp;provide responses, which we visualized. Voila! We built consensus. The results were for everyone to see, and rating/raking of features were clearly articulated&amp;nbsp;err... visualized !&amp;nbsp;Later, all moodboards and&amp;nbsp;designs were integrated with Opinion Polls to quickly make decisions. &amp;nbsp;We will take you through our journey with the customer, and show the different stages and visualizations that helped us get to build phase within 4 weeks within the enterprise.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-experience field--type-list-text field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Experience level:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;Beginner&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-speakers field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Speaker(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;mohan@azrisolutions.com&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-og-vocabulary field--type-entityreference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Session Track:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Session Tracks (Drupal GovCon 2015)&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/session-tracks-drupal-govcon-2015/business-and-strategy&quot;&gt;Business and Strategy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
